{
  "stem": "23155.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We also took some groceries, like sugar, and cream of the wheat, and dry goods.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then we arrived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Again, they put us into a, an armory, and where they went through our things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they would tell you where you have to go, to which armory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They, they divided the people-- the younger ones, the older ones, the sick ones, and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So I ended up, it was called the [INAUDIBLE] Armory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "There were, there were sick people and older people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I worked there as a helper in a, a hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I was like a junior nurse, I would say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I would wash the patients.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And in the morning, I would come in and-- mostly older men.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they would call me Sunshine, because I always had a smile on my face.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And so I made their day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And my mother worked as a nurse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I met them after.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I don't remember how long I didn't see them-- a few weeks probably.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And then I met them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "My, my mother was a nurse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And she nursed at-- there was scarlet fever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So she was a nurse in scarlet fever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And my brother, he made wooden toys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They had like a little factory going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And that's what he was doing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We didn't see each other very often.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Probably once a week, I would go there in the evening and just chat with my mother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And, and transports were coming every week, at first only from Bohemia, Moravia, but then they started coming from Germany, and from Holland, and from Denmark, and from Austria.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And it was the Tower of Babel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It was a very surrealistic place, to me at least, the way I looked at it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Because you see so many scenes which were out of the ordinary.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
